---
---
<div class="ftopbar">
  <div>
    <h3>Semaine 12 — 17–23 mars 2026</h3>
    <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--txt3);margin-top:3px">28 trades · généré dim. 23h00</div>
  </div>
  <button class="btn-p" style="font-size:11px;padding:7px 14px">📄 Export PDF</button>
</div>

<div class="fstats" style="margin-bottom:14px">
  <div class="fstat"><div class="fstat-lbl">P&L net</div><div class="fstat-val text-g">+$1 840</div><div class="fstat-sub"><span class="fup">▲ +14%</span></div></div>
  <div class="fstat"><div class="fstat-lbl">Win rate</div><div class="fstat-val text-b">67%</div><div class="fstat-sub"><span class="fup">▲ +3pts</span></div></div>
  <div class="fstat"><div class="fstat-lbl">Trades</div><div class="fstat-val">28</div><div class="fstat-sub"><span style="color:var(--green);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px">19W</span><span style="color:var(--red);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px">9L</span></div></div>
  <div class="fstat"><div class="fstat-lbl">Score</div><div class="fstat-val">74<span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--txt3)">/100</span></div><div class="fstat-sub"><span class="fup">▲ +2pts</span></div></div>
</div>

<div class="deb-ai">
  <div class="deb-ai-lbl"><div class="ai-dot-anim"></div>Analyse IA — résumé de semaine</div>
  <div class="deb-ai-txt">Bonne semaine. Tu as <strong>respecté tes stops à 100%</strong> — une première en 6 semaines. Ton talon d'Achille reste le <span class="warn">jeudi après-midi</span> : 4 trades sur 5 perdants entre 15h–17h. Si tu corriges ce créneau, ton win rate structurel dépasse <span class="good">72%</span> dès la semaine prochaine.</div>
</div>

<div class="fgrid2">
  <div>
    <div style="font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--txt3);letter-spacing:.7px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px">✅ Points forts</div>
    <div class="pts-row"><span class="dbadge-g">Force</span><div class="pts-txt" style="margin-left:8px">Stops respectés sur <strong style="color:var(--txt)">100%</strong> des 28 trades.</div></div>
    <div class="pts-row"><span class="dbadge-g">Force</span><div class="pts-txt" style="margin-left:8px">Breakouts BTC avec RR moyen de <strong style="color:var(--txt)">2.4</strong>.</div></div>
    <div class="pts-row"><span class="dbadge-g">Force</span><div class="pts-txt" style="margin-left:8px">Session London : <strong style="color:var(--txt)">78% win rate</strong> cette semaine.</div></div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <div style="font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--txt3);letter-spacing:.7px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px">⚠️ Points faibles</div>
    <div class="pts-row"><span class="dbadge-r">Critique</span><div class="pts-txt" style="margin-left:8px">Jeudi 15h–17h : <strong style="color:var(--txt)">1W / 4L</strong>. Fatigue fin de session.</div></div>
    <div class="pts-row"><span class="dbadge-y">Attention</span><div class="pts-txt" style="margin-left:8px">Vendredi matin : overtrading — <strong style="color:var(--txt)">3 trades inutiles</strong>.</div></div>
    <div class="pts-row"><span class="dbadge-y">Attention</span><div class="pts-txt" style="margin-left:8px">GBP/USD : 3ème semaine en perte. <strong style="color:var(--txt)">À éviter</strong>.</div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div style="margin-top:12px">
  <div style="font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono);color:var(--txt3);letter-spacing:.7px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px">🎯 Objectifs semaine 13 — générés par IA</div>
  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px">
    <div class="obj-box"><div class="obj-circle">○</div><div><div class="obj-title">Stopper après 15h le jeudi</div><div class="obj-meta">Pattern 1W/4L détecté 3 semaines.</div></div></div>
    <div class="obj-box"><div class="obj-circle">○</div><div><div class="obj-title">Max 4 trades le vendredi matin</div><div class="obj-meta">Prévenir l'overtrading post-gain.</div></div></div>
    <div class="obj-box"><div class="obj-circle">○</div><div><div class="obj-title">Éviter GBP/USD</div><div class="obj-meta">Win rate trop faible — 3ème semaine.</div></div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<style is:global>
  .deb-ai { background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(59,130,246,.08),rgba(139,92,246,.08)); border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,.15); border-radius:10px; padding:16px; margin-bottom:14px; }
  .deb-ai-lbl { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:7px; font-size:10px; font-family:var(--mono); color:var(--blue2); letter-spacing:.5px; margin-bottom:10px; }
  .ai-dot-anim { width:6px; height:6px; background:var(--blue); border-radius:50%; animation:blink 2s ease infinite; flex-shrink:0; }
  .deb-ai-txt { font-size:12px; color:var(--txt2); line-height:1.75; }
  .deb-ai-txt strong { color:var(--txt); }
  .deb-ai-txt .warn { color:var(--yel); }
  .deb-ai-txt .good { color:var(--green); }
  .obj-box { background:var(--bg3); border:1px solid var(--b); border-radius:8px; padding:10px 12px; display:flex; gap:9px; align-items:flex-start; margin-bottom:6px; }
  .obj-circle { width:18px; height:18px; border-radius:50%; border:1.5px solid var(--txt3); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:9px; color:var(--txt3); flex-shrink:0; margin-top:1px; }
  .obj-title { font-size:12px; font-weight:500; margin-bottom:2px; }
  .obj-meta { font-size:10px; color:var(--txt3); }
  .dbadge-g { background:rgba(16,185,129,.1); color:var(--green); border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.2); font-size:9px; font-family:var(--mono); padding:2px 7px; border-radius:4px; flex-shrink:0; }
  .dbadge-r { background:rgba(239,68,68,.1); color:var(--red); border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.2); font-size:9px; font-family:var(--mono); padding:2px 7px; border-radius:4px; flex-shrink:0; }
  .dbadge-y { background:rgba(245,158,11,.1); color:var(--yel); border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.2); font-size:9px; font-family:var(--mono); padding:2px 7px; border-radius:4px; flex-shrink:0; }
  .pts-row { display:flex; gap:8px; padding:9px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(99,155,255,.05); align-items:flex-start; }
  .pts-row:last-child { border:none; }
  .pts-txt { font-size:11px; color:var(--txt2); line-height:1.5; flex:1; }
</style>
